title: A Poem by Wingo
author: Mechjoeman
pages:
#- Mech
Oh Mech
You are like totally
Darkness incarnate
You are the shade of the night
Mech you are like the mistress of slaves of torment
And I am in constant torment
The torment that surrounds me
#- Is like a blade cursed by the virgin touch of ten thousand demons
Mech
You are that blade.
#- 